{"tid":15660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過期有折你買唔買？丹麥過期食品超市極受歡迎","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T16:16:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0949ad2189785b4792c95db9cbaba4d8fbba4a48","tid":15660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"丹麥哥本哈根一家專賣剩餘品的超市「Wefood」，店內架上的商品大多數都是即期、過期品，或者是包裝損壞的瑕疵品，甚至還有沒機會上市的淘汰原型商品，在哥本哈根聲名大噪，已經紅到開了一家分店。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥學生Signe接受法新設採訪表示，她會來這裡購物是因為支持剩餘食物轉賣的計畫，「我覺得很棒，他們不把東西丟掉而拿來販賣，來就是支持件好事。」<br />\n<br />\n Wefood計畫領導人麥登（Bassel Hmeidan）表示，店內的商品幾乎都是廠商主動提供，來源包含進出口商與當地的超市，並由Wefood員工前往取貨以提高廠商供應意願。Wefood所有的員工都是義工，且全部的利潤都捐給慈善機構。<br />\n<br />\n 在丹麥販賣過期食品是合法的，不過賣家必須標明已過期，且食品不能對人體健康有危害，麥登表示「我們看，我們聞，我們去感覺產品而判斷它是否還能消耗。」"},{"pid":"45c94260e02c6fefc12c219b8b66342f03f1ecce","tid":15660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952044228498612a7b891308764c75cb2469af12","tid":15660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4423a4d8f227ef7fadcbdcabaa5fc35749cb45fb","tid":15660,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"有時過左期一個月都照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fc752cb968a500e8903166e6269e39338330a1","tid":15660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbe1e9b79cbe7e1976928d136b180c5fc600252","tid":15660,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"係惠康買左過期野食，<br />\n<br />\n打開臭ge, 報左食環<br />\n拎左去化驗，應該就有結果&hellip;"},{"pid":"5af195886d7f5012e4fa6594d8358a6243ccd528","tid":15660,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係惠康買左過期野食，<br />\n<br />\n打開臭ge, 報左食環<br />\n拎左去化驗，應該就有結果&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原價買&hellip; 打去話退重要死唔應"},{"pid":"789a64726cac9e36cb66665409d86113959e54b9","tid":15660,"uid":4825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"我見過入面有壞左嘅栗子<br />\n本來真空包裝脹到枕頭咁<br />\n咪又係咁賣，仲有好多生果<br />\n壞到有酒味都特價照賣"},{"pid":"a745b911f55c354f69f1ab3ddfed77e801b9f1e3","tid":15660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}